{"meta":{"title":"75のBlog","subtitle":"nothing","description":"开摆","author":755,"url":"http://example.com","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"文章分类","date":"2022-11-11T13:31:37.000Z","updated":"2022-11-11T13:44:04.793Z","comments":true,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"hexo搭建Blog","slug":"hexo搭建Blog","date":"2022-11-11T12:32:20.000Z","updated":"2022-11-11T14:03:18.886Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/11/11/hexo搭建Blog/","link":"","permalink":"http://example.com/2022/11/11/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BABlog/","excerpt":"搭建简易的Blog","text":"搭建简易的Blog 1. 环境 node.js 2. 安装hexo1npm install hexo-cli -g 3. 建站 初始化本地仓库 1hexo init [文件名称] 下载依赖根据提示，前往[文件名称]目录下，下载依赖 1234npm install # 提交到git仓库的插件(遇到error:not git时)npm install hexo-deployer-git --save 启动项目此时项目已经创建好，在目录中找到_config.yml文件，滑到最后找到并修改 123456# Deployment## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deploymentdeploy: type: git repo: 你的仓库SSH地址 branch: master(github默认分支为main,gitee为master，自行修改) 清除、生成、上传完成以上以上步骤，Blog则已经创建完成，执行如下的：清除、生成、上传命令 123456789# 清除缓存hexo clean # 生成页面hexo g# 上传更新到git仓库中# 注意：这一步必须要执行下载依赖中的第二条命令hexo d","categories":[{"name":"个人blog","slug":"个人blog","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BAblog/"}],"tags":[{"name":"学习","slug":"学习","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"}]},{"title":"755のBlog","slug":"hello-world","date":"2022-11-11T08:35:28.713Z","updated":"2022-11-11T12:39:30.915Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/11/11/hello-world/","link":"","permalink":"http://example.com/2022/11/11/hello-world/","excerpt":"","text":"该学习了","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"水","slug":"水","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/%E6%B0%B4/"}]}],"categories":[{"name":"个人blog","slug":"个人blog","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BAblog/"}],"tags":[{"name":"学习","slug":"学习","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"},{"name":"水","slug":"水","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/%E6%B0%B4/"}]}